-1 builder coder Application apply~
Generally speaking, when we need help here on Distortions of Chaos, we'll
seek it out ourselves.  However, if you wish to apply for a position, the
following are good guidelines.

First, play a while.  Get to know the mud.  Make sure you like it here and
have a good understanding of the world and gameplay.  Don't bother submiting
